# TrackIt

A simple command-line app designed to help users track their personal finances. It allows users to log income and expenses, calculate and view current balance, and keep a history of transactions.

---

## Project Goals

- Allows users to log income and expenses in specific categories
- Keep a running balance
- Show a history of transactions from past months
- Save/Load data from files

---

## Task List 

- [] Create a menu system for specific user interaction
- [] Store transactions using lists or dictionaries
- [] Keep track of balance
- [] Show transaction history with timestamps of specific months and years
- [] Add save/load data from a file either using a text or JSON file

